nodes.text: This unidentified individual was a male Xexto podracer who resided on the planet Muunilinst.

In 0 ABY, the Xexto was among the five podracers who raced against the Rebel pilot Luke Skywalker, the capital city of Muunilinst. During the race, the lower left engine of the Xexto's podracer, a quad-engined Balta-Trabaat BT310, careened into the side of the cliff. The engine exploded along with the podracer, and it is not known whether the Xexto survived or not.
